Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:45.21,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,490)}Ep. 26 - I Fell Ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:49.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister! Sister. Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:53.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara! Wake up, please, Clara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What do you want, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, it's me, Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:00.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:02.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? It's not even morning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:05.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy looks a bit strange. Can you come and see? 
Comment: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:12.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Looks strange? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She has a fever and seems to be in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And even talking through delirium!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:17.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Delirium?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May. Lucy-May, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's a terrible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:38.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:42.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, light a candle. And wake mom up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:53.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the night,\NLucy developed a terrible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She was even talking in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, she kept begging for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up please, Doctor Deighton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor, please!\NWe need you to wake up, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:16.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry. I didn't mean to wake you as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? So suddenly?\NShe was all well when she went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton!\NWake up, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy suddenly fell ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:31.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:35.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where the sudden illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is she, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... There are certainly some crackles in the lungs... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what does that mean for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:58.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Her condition is anything but normal.\NNeed to bring the fever down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, speaking through delirium again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:33.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. Yes.\NThis oughta knock the fever down fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I brought more cold water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me change that water now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping now. Seems like she's still in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If fever subsides by morning, she'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:06.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can be free now.\NReturn to sleep in the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She still speaks in her sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. Well, go back to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:10.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who is she apologizing to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:28.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy took it to heart when I dropped my textbook on Latin grammar into the river because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My book!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:41.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I succeeded! You should've seen your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:55.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can trust me and your mother\Nto look after Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She's on the verge of pneumonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she suddenly develop such a fever, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can only surmise it's because of a physical weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She was so full of life during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I think of it, in the evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She barely touched her dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, we'll be in trouble\Nif her fever doesn't subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some special way?\NA way to knock down the fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the fever medicine\Nthat I gave her before takes effect. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we just need to keep cooling her down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:43.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NDoctor, thanks a lot for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call upon you again if there's any development.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But until then, please feel free to have your rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Some development happening is my only wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think, she'll probably be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's the energetic girl Lucy-May we all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was always unthinkable to me\Nthat Lucy-May could ever fall ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, there are no people who never fall ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go catch a shuteye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:21.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you also grow big, this box\Nwill probably become too cramped for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We need to build you a proper house soon\Nfor you to dwell in once you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing serious happened to Lucy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once the fever subsides,\Nshe'll be her usual self again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:49.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's unthinkable for a girl that lively\Nto end up dying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Normally, you'd think it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, is that to say\NLucy's illness is not "normal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That talking in delirium worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:08:01.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But normally, anyone would speak in his sleep\Nwhen he develops a high-grade fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's odd is her repeating\Nthe very same words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry" - nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:10.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I told her long ago - I forgave her already,\Nfor the book and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:11.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sick people who don't strive\Nto get better end up dying. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you don't mean to say... Lucy, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:26.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, in children,\Na desire to get better soon prevails.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:31.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in Lucy-May's case,\Nif her heart is besieged by worries,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:34.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,it takes a toll on her body as well,\Nresulting in a high-grade fever and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:38.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I... But I... forgave Lucy already. It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forgive her from your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:46.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The hard fact that she caused the loss of a book so dear to you is the only thing that Lucy-May remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is,\Nafter you said you'd forgiven her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,could something in your behavior\Nhave betrayed your true feelings? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:56.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something came to your mind? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:15.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't equate Lucy-May's usual cheerfulness and frivolousness with insensitiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:20.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She saw it right through that you weren't sincere\Nwith yourself when you said you forgave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She may have perked up on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:27.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but deep in her heart, she kept brooding\Nover the depth of her guilt before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:35.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that after that happened, I feel like I couldn't help treating Lucy in a colder manner than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means I'm the reason\Nfor Lucy's current illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, don't be jumping to conclusions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May's illness was caused by a common cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:14.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, among the reasons\Nwhy she almost developed a pneumonia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:18.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,was this heavy burden of responsibility\Nshe has to carry in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's about all you need to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:25.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So to make thinks better I just need to relieve\Nher heart of this heavy burden, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only you can, do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I wanted to go get some more sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, are you really that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're one kind kid, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... Forgive me, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you have to eat, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy won't come. She's ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She still has a high-grade fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,so she can't show up outside for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, eat now, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:09.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what would be the thing\NLucy wants the most now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:13.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She already has Little as her pet.\NIsn't that quite enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Lucy thinks this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe there's something outside animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:22.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... What in the world\Ncould that girl be wanting to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:28.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You want to eat something, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:33.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Doctor Deighton advised for you\Nto eat at least something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like eating anything.
Comment: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mr. Popple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I have some business with Doctor Deighton today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So? How about I nap for a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:20.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, my master insisted\Non you coming to see him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand pardons,\Nbut who might your master be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, you have a rather poor memory\Nfor your age, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Adam. And my master is Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Ah, right, right, I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, will you be so kind as to follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Explain to me Mr. Pettywell's complaints first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:41.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. He's been in great pain since last night,\Nand couldn't eat anything in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Got a naughty stomach, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:45.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, is it his waist again? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of your riddles!\NJust tell me where!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:51.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's his tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here. His tooth hurts since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go home, you dunce.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was telling my Master the same thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Doctor Deighton is by no means a dentist."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Master replied, instead:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:12.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"If you summon that quack to my place,\Nhe'll come this instant, wiggling his tail!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:16.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't got no tail.\NNow, 'bout time you left, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. In that case, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:24.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... After all I've done, calling me a quack!\NDamn this jerk Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come right away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:52.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About that, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You told him I'd compensate\Nhim generously, didn't you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:59.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton said, because he is no dentist,\Nhe can't provide you with a proper treatment, sir... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:00.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Master, I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:03.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with Deighton's insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:11.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'm not counting on him for anything, ever again.\NWill find someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is she? The fever is still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still pretty hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could knock the fever down...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:33.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I can't listen\Nto this delirious murmur any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:39.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So? How is Lucy looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Still that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Started talking in her sleep again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:55.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom even said she's fed up.\NShe doesn't want to hear it ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say that, too... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pansy. Pansy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:27.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll help you drink in a moment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The water is tasty. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:17:00.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, since I'm already here,\Nwould you mind listening to me for a bit? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the end of the day,\NI wasn't acting like a man should.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:10.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While you had a high fever,\Nyou were talking in your sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:12.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:17.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it from Kate. I kept saying\N"I'm sorry" and "forgive me," didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:22.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You were probably still recalling that time,\Nwhen my textbook on Latin grammar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you've already forgiven me for it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I really intended to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But somewhere inside, I still had that sentiment,\Nscreaming "can't forgive."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I can swear now. I {\i1}really{\i0} forgave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer hold any grudges. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:47.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:53.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I just recalled that there was something\NI promised to make for you when we were in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:55.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:17:59.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:01.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:03.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and fulfill that promise right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:04.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon, so we can fly that kite together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my bad! My bad, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have tired you with talking. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:17.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll get to making it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:27.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make it sooner.\NThis way, you'll also get better sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going then, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! What's wrong, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, you'd better return to sleeping quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:04.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:10.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please help Lucy get better\Nas soon as you seem possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:13.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, of course I will. However, for that,\Nthe fever has to subside first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It subsided a bit, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go check on her real quick!\NReally? Subsided?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:31.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, please! It hurts so much,\NI feel I could die! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die from a caries. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At least try to look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine I looked at it:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:40.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh? This looks like a cavity in the tooth.\NMust be a caries. Hurts bad, I imagine!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That said, I can't treat it anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever, just look at it, whatever comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Waah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:51.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it hurts, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do something to stop this pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay any money!\NBut please, do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever problem you encounter,\Nyou start putting out money. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch! It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the first thing about dentistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:12.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But back when I was a kid,\Nmom used to yank out any hurting teeth we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suggest yanking it out?\NI will never agree to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was about the only thing I could do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I need to see my patient now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a moment. Moment, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It hurts! Hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:38.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Deighton quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:40.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch-ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Hey! You're in the way, you rogue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:49.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd ever think this is a good place to sleep at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:56.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sticky. Let's go get some fresh grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pansy, you come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:20.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,These are the last for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:22.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:27.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any more special errands for me\Nto run today, I'd like some free time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't mind. What will you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to build a kite,\Nso I'll go fetch some bamboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:33.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need to give it to Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:27.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!\NDoctor! Doctor Deighton!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:32.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Doctor! Yank it out!\NI can't stand this pain no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:35.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, in that case, I'll need a pair of pincers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:36.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure Ben had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:38.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:41.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't rush me.\NI'm getting the pincers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:43.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Oh, found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:43.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:45.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, open your mouth wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I count on you to be gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:50.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:51.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:52.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Open wider now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:54.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:58.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:22:59.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:02.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May is acting strange.\NPlease. Please come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? That sounds urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:06.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You, hold this for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:08.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:13.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! It hurts so much! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:39.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:43.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Carried away by thoughts of Lucy's illness,\NI was already dozing off, when suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:46.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Little's distressed shrieking. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:51.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:55.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was awfully startled, so I dashed towards\Nwhere his shrieking was coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.59,0:23:59.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:07.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember for how long exactly\NI had been asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:09.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but I remember riding a kite through the sky! 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:11.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it wasn't just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:14.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Riding the Kite".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:16.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
